## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023, and some sources may have more recent updates that are not included. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant findings from non-English publications. The complexity of climate change impacts means that this report provides a general overview rather than an exhaustive analysis of all potential health effects.

